{"type":"article","id":2904,"title":"六四屠城图片全览 第三编：六四血腥大屠城(一)","uid":16,"topics":[149,998],"contents":"6月3日10时48分木樨地一辆戒严吉普车撞死一人创伤四人<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/Ljw8eHr.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Ljw8eHr.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Ljw8eHr.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/c3xAZS0.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/c3xAZS0.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/c3xAZS0.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n1989年6月3日10时杨建利博士因八九年“六四”时返回中国大陆声援天安门广场学运，随后遭大陆当局列为拒绝入境的四十九人黑名单。2002年4月回国被捕<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/GGFD5tC.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/GGFD5tC.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/GGFD5tC.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n联合报报道当时天安门广场已混进数千便衣部队，伺机扩大事端，以便制造军队镇压的借口<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/nH6S3G5.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/nH6S3G5.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/nH6S3G5.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n长安街上，载满军人的军车正开往天安门<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/ytnwhv8.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ytnwhv8.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/ytnwhv8.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n恐怖屠城开始了!!!<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/iPiaaaf.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/iPiaaaf.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/iPiaaaf.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n六三下午，一个工人被人大会堂前的军警打伤﹐在群众的帮助下出来。他手里的钢盔是在冲突中一个士兵掉下的<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/YBwjI9C.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/YBwjI9C.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/YBwjI9C.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n向死难的三市民致哀<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/v8lbFiB.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/v8lbFiB.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/v8lbFiB.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n六月三日，大量不知事的「娃娃兵」跑步冲入北京市区.<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/JJMCNhv.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JJMCNhv.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/JJMCNhv.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n一名学生（右）拉住一名士兵，劝他别去天安门广场<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/N3XKfKC.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/N3XKfKC.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/N3XKfKC.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n六月三日晚间，台湾学生与北京天安门学生进行「血脉相连，两岸对歌」活动，六月四日清晨，对岸突然没了音讯，原来屠杀已经开始。马英九回忆当时中广主持人大喊：「天哪，他们真的开枪了！」<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/00eQM33.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/00eQM33.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/00eQM33.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n六月四日凌晨2时35分，「民主女神」像成为中共戒严部队进入天安门广场后首先动手的目标－－戒严部队的士兵合力将她拉倒，并且以电视摄影机拍摄拉倒的过程，当天即在中央电视台播放出来<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/3qq3YYM.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3qq3YYM.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/3qq3YYM.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n民主女神像被中共戒严部队合力拉倒<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/Kp8HgXO.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Kp8HgXO.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Kp8HgXO.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n士兵跳过广场路障<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/wwwg6dS.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/wwwg6dS.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/wwwg6dS.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n六四凌晨，从人民大会堂冲来的戒严士兵平端着枪对着广场学生扫射!<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/JO5mcgY.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JO5mcgY.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/JO5mcgY.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n坦克大军疯狂扫射......<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/Hs5yYim.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Hs5yYim.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Hs5yYim.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n杨建利博士因八九年“六四”时返回中国大陆声援天安门广场学运，随后遭大陆当局列为拒绝入境的四十九人黑名单。背景为六三子夜冲入广场被焚烧的装甲车<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/1oZUPLi.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1oZUPLi.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/1oZUPLi.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n装甲车强行开进广场疯狂射杀，北京市民围在尸体旁发誓要向政府讨回公道<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/sYYxs6m.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/sYYxs6m.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/sYYxs6m.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n军队向广场上的学生开抢扫射，几位男同学扶着一位受伤女同学赶往医院<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/0OopXiv.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0OopXiv.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/0OopXiv.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/wBf9CY6.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/wBf9CY6.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/wBf9CY6.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n含着眼泪，部分学生们撤离广场(六四凌晨五时)<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/YAqDACY.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/YAqDACY.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/YAqDACY.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n一个孩子哭着抓起碎砖要掷向运兵车，被旁边的学生们劝止<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/eQRjYC5.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/eQRjYC5.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/eQRjYC5.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n坦克追碾从广场撤离的学生队伍，六部口坦克下的冤魂无数。六四早上军队在长安街上扫射，市民英勇抵抗。照片中可见满街尸体的长安街上，其它人在抢救伤员<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/S2Az8xO.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/S2Az8xO.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/S2Az8xO.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n坦克下的冤魂<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/ta4ogpN.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ta4ogpN.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/ta4ogpN.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n军队清理现场，毁尸灭迹<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/nlSh6xE.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/nlSh6xE.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/nlSh6xE.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n北京大屠杀（六月三日二十二时至六月五日零时）<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/7HOwYrs.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7HOwYrs.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/7HOwYrs.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n坦克后的尸鸿遍野！<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/49q099X.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/49q099X.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/49q099X.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n被烧的军车——海淀六四上午海淀路人大附近<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/AnowcDo.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/AnowcDo.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/AnowcDo.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n6月4日摄于长安大街的广播电影电视部楼前被焚烧的军车<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/AjclzeN.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/AjclzeN.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/AjclzeN.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n“许多人子弹打到身上﹐都还以为是橡皮子弹﹗”<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/hAxECVk.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/hAxECVk.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/hAxECVk.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/MWOWYxC.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MWOWYxC.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/MWOWYxC.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n“人民子弟兵”向人民开枪，群众奋勇冒死抢救伤者<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/8ffNYMw.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8ffNYMw.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/8ffNYMw.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n大屠杀之日天亮后，天安门附近布满学生的尸体和自行车残骸（美联社照片）<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/qmjNWtz.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qmjNWtz.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/qmjNWtz.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/BydnUKV.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/BydnUKV.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/BydnUKV.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-07-31","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":0}